channel.description:
For those of you that dont know exactly what this is its a button to add items in your stored b.o.b or summoning npcs "custom" bank to your inventory automatically. Okay lets move on.

In PlayerAssistant.java add this [code]public void removeBoBItems(int slot, int amount) {
		if (c.getItems().freeSlots() > 0) {
			c.getItems().addItem(c.storeditems[slot], amount);
			c.occupied[slot] = false;
			c.storeditems[slot] = 0;
			c.getItems().resetTempItems();
			c.getItems().resetBank();
			c.totalstored -= slot;
		} else {
			c.getItems().resetTempItems();
			c.getItems().resetBank();
			c.sendMessage("Not enough space in your inventory.");
			return;
		}
	}[/code]
Now this part depends on what button you decide to choose to take b.o.b but here is mine.
